            ],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "无声铃鹿",
            "Text": "是啊，如果是和训练员一起看……\n一定会是片更美的景色。",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "",
            "Text": "我边看着眼前的小小雪景──\n边和无声铃鹿闲聊着。",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "无声铃鹿",
            "Text": "嗯，请务必试试。",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
